name: Power Rangers 2: Zeo vs. Machine Empire
name_original: Power Rangers 2: Zeo vs. Machine Empire
description:
Power Rangers 2: Zeo vs. Machine Empire is an arcade game developed by CyberFlix. It was originally released in 1996. It was published by GTE Entertainment. The game is rated as "Meh" on RAWG.
You can play Power Rangers 2: Zeo vs. Machine Empire on PC.
